  "title": "Hotel Cleaner [Somerset | 6 days | up to $2000] - LCYL",
  "description": "<h3><strong>Hotel Cleaner</strong></h3><p><strong>6 days, 8am- 4pm</strong></p><p><strong>Salary: $1800-$2000</strong></p><p><strong>Location: Kramat Rd, Singapore 228750 (Somerset)</strong></p><p><u><strong>Job scope:</strong></u></p><ul><li>Clean and tidy up hotel rooms.</li><li>Dust and polish various surfaces and furniture</li><li>Vacuum, sweep, and mop floors</li><li>Empty trash bins</li><li>Change linens and towels and replace toiletries.</li><li>Collaborate with the housekeeping team to complete the daily cleaning schedule.</li><li>Restock cleaning supplies in the hand cart.</li><li>Report any issues that require maintenance.</li></ul><p><br /></p><p>Cheong Yeat Long | R25145358</p><p>The Supreme HR Advisory Pte Ltd | EA 14C7279</p>",
